gujarati.context:
Wherever the party stayed for some time, that place remained unspoiled; 
Thus they stayed and gave alms, Shyam saw; 
They themselves came to Jetpur village.

Here is the translation:

Above is the Name of the King, kept as a sacred thing; 
This which is mine, everyone knows; but You alone know, Oh Lord.

Here is the translation:

Vasun bhushan vahnu jehe re, graham karojo aape jan tehe re;
Nij jannee poorajo haam re, karojo raksha tenee athu n jaam re.

Here is the translation of the Gujarati couplet:

In sciences, such a talk is; it's as if one is condemning Brahmin-ness; 
Whose fragrance doesn't spread from Mount Meru, why should I stay with him?

Here is the translation:

This sorrow remains in this body, great sin remains; 
Therefore, I should do self-realization, woman's body is not equal to one.
